overview: The 2023 PFL regular season gets underway in Las Vegas this weekend with Brendan Loughnane's clash with Marlon Moraes headlining the event. The co-main event meanwhile sees 2022 PFL Light Heavyweight World Champion Robert Wilkinson take on Thiago Santos who is set to make his eagerly anticipated PFL debut.
title: PFL 1: Loughnane vs. Moraes
